text: Rachael Yamala (born 12 February 1975) is a former football midfielder. Yamala played for the Nigeria women's national football team. In 1991, she was in the FIFA Women's World Cup. She played for the Kakanfo Babes club in Nigeria. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Association football midfielders
